<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.7.1">
<l>piṟavit tuyaraṟa ñāṉat tuṇiṉṟu</l>
<l>tuṟavic cuṭarviḷak kantalaip peyvā</l>
<l>raṟavaṉai yāḻip paṭaiyan taṇaṉai</l>
<l>maṟaviyai yiṉṟi maṉattuvaip pārē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So that the misery of [re]birth be severed, those who, standing in the world,</l>
<l>put on [their] heads the glowing lamp of renunciation</l>
<l>without forgettfulness will put in [their] minds</l>
<l>the gracious one with the discus weapon on the serpent bed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
